<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='300040' id='t-300040'>So as we ponder the future,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='303280' id='t-303280'>know that your future
